OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,FIsrael's military has struck southern
OL,7,FLebanon overnight, threatening a
OL,8,Ffreshly signed agreement between the
OL,9,FUS and Iran to end all conflict in the
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,FAt least 16 people were killed in
OL,13,FIsraeli airstrikes on Friday morning,
OL,14,Faccording to Lebanon's state-run
OL,15,FNational News Agency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
