OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,FThe Israeli Defence Forces said they
OL,7,Fwere strikes against "terrorists and
OL,8,Fterrorist infrastructure of the
OL,9,Fterrorist organisation Hezbollah",
OL,10,Fwhich came after the group's "repeated
OL,11,Fviolations" of the ceasefire agreement.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
