OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781911153
OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump and Iranian
OL,7,FPresident Masoud Pezeshkian both
OL,8,Fsigned an agreement on Wednesday,
OL,9,Fwhich called for the "immediate and
OL,10,Fpermanent" end of military operations
OL,11,Fon "all fronts", including Lebanon.
OL,13,FBut Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,14,FNetanyahu, who faces elections later
OL,15,Fthis year, has refused to withdraw,
OL,16,Fstating that the nation's forces will
OL,17,Fremain in Lebanon until the threat
OL,18,Ffrom Hezbollah has been eliminated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
