PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781911153
OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,FUS Vice President JD Vance was due to
OL,7,Ftravel to Switzerland on Thursday to
OL,8,Flead talks with Iran, but the trip has
OL,9,Fbeen delayed.
OL,11,FReports from Hezbollah-linked media
OL,12,Fhave claimed this is because Iran has
OL,13,Fdelayed sending its delegation, due to
OL,14,FIsraeli's continued strikes in Lebanon.
OL,16,FThe White House said Vance and his
OL,17,Fdelegation were prepared for talks,
OL,18,Fbut were unable to finalise the plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
