PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781911153
OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,F"The logistics of these negotiations
OL,7,Fhave never been simple or
OL,8,Fpredictable," the statement read.
OL,10,FIran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah
OL,11,FMojtaba Khamenei had previously
OL,12,Fendorsed direct negotiations with the
OL,13,FUS in a statement read by state media.
OL,15,F"It is obvious that the face-to-face
OL,16,Fnegotiations that will be held in the
OL,17,Ffuture will not mean accepting the
OL,18,Fenemy's opinion," Khamenei said in his
OL,19,Fstatement.
OL,26,@zD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
