PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781911153
OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,FVance appeared to lash out at the
OL,7,FIsraeli government on Thursday,
OL,8,Fwarning them that Trump is the "only
OL,9,Fhead of state in the entire world who
OL,10,Fis sympathetic to the nation of Israel
OL,11,Fat this moment in time".
OL,13,FHe said Netanyahu, "to his credit, has
OL,14,Fnot gone down this path" of standing
OL,15,Fagainst the deal, but blamed members
OL,16,Fof his cabinet.
OL,26,@uD@TOUvD@XO]
