OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781911153
OL,3,CIsrael strikes Lebanon overnight as US-
OL,4,CIran talks in Switzerland delayed
OL,6,FThe signing of the US-Iran agreement
OL,7,Ftook immediate effect once it was
OL,8,Fsigned, and kick-started a 60-day
OL,9,Fnegotiating period between Tehran and
OL,10,FWashington.
OL,12,FIt waives several US-backed sanctions
OL,13,Fon Iran, allowing the country to sell
OL,14,Fits oil freely, and calls for Tehran
OL,15,Fto dilute its stockpile of highly
OL,16,Fenriched uranium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
